                    <name>richTextValue</name>
                    <value>&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;font-size: 22px; color: rgb(230, 0, 0);&quot;&gt;B2B Commerce on Lightning Experience&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;This app is used to administer B2B Commerce on Lightning Experience,&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;a complete commerce experience all in Lightning. Be able to browse and search for simple products, view product detail information, add to cart, and perform checkout. B2B Commerce on Lightning Experience uses standard objects (Price Books, Product, Orders).&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;The B2B Commerce on Lightning Experience storefront is in the &lt;b&gt;B2B Commerce Lightning Experience &lt;/b&gt;Community and can be accessible by user &lt;b&gt;Lauren Bailey.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b&gt;Get Started with demoing B2B Commerce here: &lt;/b&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://solutionscentral.io/topics/1284b030-6221-11ea-8b61-7dbc3724e03a/b2b-commerce/&quot; rel=&quot;noopener noreferrer&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot;&gt;https://solutionscentral.io/topics/1284b030-6221-11ea-8b61-7dbc3724e03a/b2b-commerce/&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px; color: rgb(15, 15, 15);&quot;&gt;Post Setup Steps&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Index Search for the Storefront&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Go to store: &lt;b&gt;B2B Commerce Lightning Experience&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on &lt;b&gt;Search&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;On the &lt;b&gt;Search Index Summary&lt;/b&gt; screen click &lt;b&gt;Rebuild Index&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Publish the &lt;b&gt;B2B Commerce Lightning Experience &lt;/b&gt;community&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(240, 2, 2);&quot;&gt;NOTE: In Experience Builder there are instructions regarding updates to certain components that will be needed to setup the demo.&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Disable Triggers&amp;nbsp;&amp;nbsp;in &lt;b&gt;Salesforce Billing&lt;/b&gt;&lt;ol&gt;&lt;li&gt;Goto &lt;b&gt;Setup&lt;/b&gt; &amp;gt; &lt;b&gt;Installed Packages&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;Click on &lt;b&gt;Configure&lt;/b&gt; for Salesforce Billing&lt;/li&gt;&lt;li&gt;&lt;b&gt;Enable&lt;/b&gt;&amp;nbsp;for&lt;b&gt;&amp;nbsp;Disable Triggers&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;/li&gt;&lt;/ol&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;b style=&quot;font-size: 16px;&quot;&gt;Checkout&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;If wanting to demo a credit card transaction in checkout, select &lt;b&gt;Visa&lt;/b&gt; and enter the following number: &lt;b style=&quot;color: rgb(0, 0, 0); background-color: transparent;&quot;&gt;4111111111111111&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/p&gt;&lt;p&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;</value>
